data.description: Solid brick bungalow with all appliances! This 4 bedroom, 1.5 bath home is freshly painted and ready to go. The first floor living and dining rooms both have hardwood floors. The two bedrooms on the first floor are nicely sized and have ceiling fans. The main bathroom is located between the two bedrooms. Upstairs are two very large bedrooms. The main bedroom also has an attached half bath with new cabinet and flooring. The furnace and AC were replaced in 2014, the kitchen appliances were replaced in 2020, and the washer and dryer were also purchased in 2020. All appliances are staying with the home. The roofs were replaced in 2010 on the house and garage. Outside you will find a nice stamped concrete patio, shaded back yard, and two car garage. POS has been completed and passed.
